    "description": "<strong>Time to play Battle Bros!</strong><br>A turn-based, card battling, tabletop hybrid. Build your deck with cards you've obtained and put together a strategy that can't be beaten. Summon your characters to the battlefield and use your cards to equip them with gear and abilities to gain the edge on your opponent. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/ff0473a9a798cd2efe64b5eaba5447de.poster.avif?t=1687748808\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/ff0473a9a798cd2efe64b5eaba5447de.webm?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/ff0473a9a798cd2efe64b5eaba5447de.mp4?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Battle Bros. combines grid-based combat and card battling elements to create a unique gameplay experience. This paired with an original setting and hand drawn art style make it a truly different kind of game to play.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/11b57645384dc95c279d27ccaf524974.poster.avif?t=1687748808\" width=600 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/11b57645384dc95c279d27ccaf524974.webm?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/11b57645384dc95c279d27ccaf524974.mp4?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><strong><i>Singleplayer:</i></strong><br>Face AI opponents, with multiple difficulties planned.<br><br><strong><i>Multiplayer:</i></strong><br>Face your friends and prove you have the better deck.<br><br><strong><i>Character Customization:</i></strong><br>Obtain different customizations and customize each of your characters for your team, including their look and stats.<br><br><strong><i>Card Collection:</i></strong><br>Earn cards through different means and collect the best cards for your deck.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/de792cb1a7289677de4282b11a74fc0e.poster.avif?t=1687748808\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/de792cb1a7289677de4282b11a74fc0e.webm?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289000/extras/de792cb1a7289677de4282b11a74fc0e.mp4?t=1687748808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
